channel.title: Rsc?
channel.description:
Well, I've searched and googled and searched some more... and well i really havent found anything about rsc anymore like i remember whne i used to play that there were soooo many rsc scripts but like now, where are they? i had some but then i formatted my pc and they were lost but someone must have one, no? Well this is just a request for old scripts that would work on the private servers running around now...
i've still got some scripts if anyone is interested theya re powerminers pwoerfishers and crappy autofighters
most of the ones i have dont work very well but if anyone wants it i can upload them to a rar file...
also if anyone knows of a bot for like rsca or something like the ausbot but ausbot is payed so i cant really get it "/ but anyways if you do have anything pelase post here =)
thanks everyone for reading this...
and dont flame me please >.<
